    "body": "Thanks to @kevingelion and @revln9 from the Slack Electron discussion, i was able to solve my issue.\r\nAll i need to use is getAppPath() and from there go to the parent folder where the data file is located:\r\n\r\n```\r\nresourcePath = path.join(app.getAppPath(), '../../../db/');\r\n```"
